data.title: Spring of 2024 President’s List
data.meta_description: Students on the Clemson University President's List demonstrate a high level of academic excellence and dedication. Here is the Spring 2024 list of students.
data.text:
Paula Powers

Share:

Securing a place on the Clemson University President’s List signifies a high level of academic excellence and dedication, making it a noteworthy achievement. This prestigious recognition is awarded to individuals who have exhibited exceptional academic prowess, maintaining a remarkable minimum 4.0-grade point average while successfully completing a minimum of 12 semester hours, exclusive of Pass/No Pass coursework.

The Spring 2024 President’s List features an impressive roster of students, arranged alphabetically by last name. This list showcases the commitment and diligence of students in their pursuit of scholarly success.

In recognition of this momentous accomplishment, students and their supporters may visit the University’s President’s and Dean’s List website. There, individuals can create a personalized badge by entering a student’s name and download the image to save, share or send.
